Moving Average, no outliers¶

In [287]:
tickers = [AAPL,IBM,JPM,DJX]
ticker_string = ['AAPL','IBM','JPM','DJX']
for i in range(len(tickers)):
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10,5))
    ax1 = fig.add_axes([0.1, 0.5, 1.1, 0.5])
    tickers[i]['Adj Close'].plot()
    tickers[i]['50 MA'].plot()
    tickers[i]['20 MA'].plot()
    tickers[i]['intersect'][tickers[i]['intersect'] > 0].plot(marker='o',linestyle='None',markersize=8, grid=True,title='{}: Moving Average, no outliers'.format(ticker_string[i]))
    plt.ylabel('Price')
    plt.legend(['Adj Close','MA50','MA20','intersection'])
    ax2 = fig.add_axes([0.1, 0.0, 1.1, 0.5])
    tickers[i]['cumulative'].plot(grid=True)
    plt.ylabel('Cumulative returns')
    plt.legend(['Cumulative returns'])
    #plt.savefig('/Users/desmond/Desktop/FSP_CW/all/Section 4/eps_files/{}_MA_no_outlier.eps'.format(ticker_string[i]),bbox_inches='tight')

start = '2018-03-16'

AAPL = data.DataReader("AAPL", 
                       start=start, 
                       end=end, 
                       data_source='yahoo')
IBM = data.DataReader("IBM", 
                       start=start, 
                       end=end,
                       data_source='yahoo')
JPM = data.DataReader("JPM", 
                       start=start, 
                       end=end,
                       data_source='yahoo')
DJX = data.DataReader("DJIA", 
                       start=start, 
                       end=end, 
                       data_source='yahoo')
In [289]:
#outliers
outliers = ['2018-05-14','2018-09-14','2018-12-14','2019-01-14']
aapl_max = AAPL['Adj Close'].max()*1.2
ibm_max = IBM['Adj Close'].max()*1.2
jpm_max = JPM['Adj Close'].max()*1.2
djx_max = DJX['Adj Close'].max()*1.2

for i in outliers:
    AAPL.loc[datetime.strptime(i,'%Y-%m-%d'),'Adj Close'] = aapl_max
    IBM.loc[datetime.strptime(i,'%Y-%m-%d'),'Adj Close'] = ibm_max
    JPM.loc[datetime.strptime(i,'%Y-%m-%d'),'Adj Close'] = jpm_max
    DJX.loc[datetime.strptime(i,'%Y-%m-%d'),'Adj Close'] = djx_max
    
#simple returns
AAPL['ret'] = AAPL['Adj Close'].pct_change()
IBM['ret'] = IBM['Adj Close'].pct_change()
JPM['ret'] = JPM['Adj Close'].pct_change()
DJX['ret'] = DJX['Adj Close'].pct_change()

#moving averages
AAPL['20 MA'] = AAPL['Adj Close'].rolling(20).mean().dropna()
AAPL['50 MA'] = AAPL['Adj Close'].rolling(50).mean().dropna()
IBM['20 MA'] = IBM['Adj Close'].rolling(20).mean().dropna()
IBM['50 MA'] = IBM['Adj Close'].rolling(50).mean().dropna()
JPM['20 MA'] = JPM['Adj Close'].rolling(20).mean().dropna()
JPM['50 MA'] = JPM['Adj Close'].rolling(50).mean().dropna()
DJX['20 MA'] = DJX['Adj Close'].rolling(20).mean().dropna()
DJX['50 MA'] = DJX['Adj Close'].rolling(50).mean().dropna()

# buy/sell action
AAPL['Action'] = np.ones(len(AAPL))*np.nan
IBM['Action'] = np.ones(len(IBM))*np.nan
JPM['Action'] = np.ones(len(JPM))*np.nan
DJX['Action'] = np.ones(len(DJX))*np.nan

AAPL.loc[AAPL['20 MA'] >= AAPL['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
AAPL.loc[AAPL['20 MA'] < AAPL['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100
IBM.loc[IBM['20 MA'] >= IBM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
IBM.loc[IBM['20 MA'] < IBM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100
JPM.loc[JPM['20 MA'] >= JPM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
JPM.loc[JPM['20 MA'] < JPM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100
DJX.loc[DJX['20 MA'] >= DJX['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
DJX.loc[DJX['20 MA'] < DJX['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100

# cumulative returns
AAPL['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(AAPL['ret']*AAPL['Action'])
IBM['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(IBM['ret']*IBM['Action'])
JPM['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(JPM['ret']*JPM['Action'])
DJX['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(DJX['ret']*DJX['Action'])

#intersection
AAPL['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))
IBM['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))
JPM['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))
DJX['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))

idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(AAPL['20 MA'][49:] - AAPL['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
AAPL['intersect'].iloc[idx] = AAPL['20 MA'].iloc[idx]
idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(IBM['20 MA'][49:] - IBM['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
IBM['intersect'].iloc[idx] = IBM['20 MA'].iloc[idx]
idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(JPM['20 MA'][49:] - JPM['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
JPM['intersect'].iloc[idx] = JPM['20 MA'].iloc[idx]
idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(DJX['20 MA'][49:] - DJX['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
DJX['intersect'].iloc[idx] = DJX['20 MA'].iloc[idx]

#simple returns
AAPL['ret'] = AAPL['Adj Close'].pct_change()
IBM['ret'] = IBM['Adj Close'].pct_change()
JPM['ret'] = JPM['Adj Close'].pct_change()
DJX['ret'] = DJX['Adj Close'].pct_change()

#rolling medians
AAPL['20 MA'] = AAPL['Adj Close'].rolling(20).median().dropna()
AAPL['50 MA'] = AAPL['Adj Close'].rolling(50).median().dropna()
IBM['20 MA'] = IBM['Adj Close'].rolling(20).median().dropna()
IBM['50 MA'] = IBM['Adj Close'].rolling(50).median().dropna()
JPM['20 MA'] = JPM['Adj Close'].rolling(20).median().dropna()
JPM['50 MA'] = JPM['Adj Close'].rolling(50).median().dropna()
DJX['20 MA'] = DJX['Adj Close'].rolling(20).median().dropna()
DJX['50 MA'] = DJX['Adj Close'].rolling(50).median().dropna()

# buy/sell action
AAPL['Action'] = np.ones(len(AAPL))*np.nan
IBM['Action'] = np.ones(len(IBM))*np.nan
JPM['Action'] = np.ones(len(JPM))*np.nan
DJX['Action'] = np.ones(len(DJX))*np.nan

AAPL.loc[AAPL['20 MA'] >= AAPL['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
AAPL.loc[AAPL['20 MA'] < AAPL['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100
IBM.loc[IBM['20 MA'] >= IBM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
IBM.loc[IBM['20 MA'] < IBM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100
JPM.loc[JPM['20 MA'] >= JPM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
JPM.loc[JPM['20 MA'] < JPM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100
DJX.loc[DJX['20 MA'] >= DJX['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
DJX.loc[DJX['20 MA'] < DJX['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100

# cumulative returns
AAPL['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(AAPL['ret']*AAPL['Action'])
IBM['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(IBM['ret']*IBM['Action'])
JPM['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(JPM['ret']*JPM['Action'])
DJX['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(DJX['ret']*DJX['Action'])

#intersection
AAPL['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))
IBM['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))
JPM['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))
DJX['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))

idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(AAPL['20 MA'][49:] - AAPL['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
AAPL['intersect'].iloc[idx] = AAPL['20 MA'].iloc[idx]
idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(IBM['20 MA'][49:] - IBM['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
IBM['intersect'].iloc[idx] = IBM['20 MA'].iloc[idx]
idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(JPM['20 MA'][49:] - JPM['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
JPM['intersect'].iloc[idx] = JPM['20 MA'].iloc[idx]
idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(DJX['20 MA'][49:] - DJX['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
DJX['intersect'].iloc[idx] = DJX['20 MA'].iloc[idx]

    IBM.loc[datetime.strptime(i,'%Y-%m-%d'),'Adj Close'] = ibm_max
    JPM.loc[datetime.strptime(i,'%Y-%m-%d'),'Adj Close'] = jpm_max
    DJX.loc[datetime.strptime(i,'%Y-%m-%d'),'Adj Close'] = djx_max
    
#simple returns
AAPL['ret'] = AAPL['Adj Close'].pct_change()
IBM['ret'] = IBM['Adj Close'].pct_change()
JPM['ret'] = JPM['Adj Close'].pct_change()
DJX['ret'] = DJX['Adj Close'].pct_change()

#rolling medians
AAPL['20 MA'] = AAPL['Adj Close'].rolling(20).median().dropna()
AAPL['50 MA'] = AAPL['Adj Close'].rolling(50).median().dropna()
IBM['20 MA'] = IBM['Adj Close'].rolling(20).median().dropna()
IBM['50 MA'] = IBM['Adj Close'].rolling(50).median().dropna()
JPM['20 MA'] = JPM['Adj Close'].rolling(20).median().dropna()
JPM['50 MA'] = JPM['Adj Close'].rolling(50).median().dropna()
DJX['20 MA'] = DJX['Adj Close'].rolling(20).median().dropna()
DJX['50 MA'] = DJX['Adj Close'].rolling(50).median().dropna()

# buy/sell action
AAPL['Action'] = np.ones(len(AAPL))*np.nan
IBM['Action'] = np.ones(len(IBM))*np.nan
JPM['Action'] = np.ones(len(JPM))*np.nan
DJX['Action'] = np.ones(len(DJX))*np.nan

AAPL.loc[AAPL['20 MA'] >= AAPL['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
AAPL.loc[AAPL['20 MA'] < AAPL['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100
IBM.loc[IBM['20 MA'] >= IBM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
IBM.loc[IBM['20 MA'] < IBM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100
JPM.loc[JPM['20 MA'] >= JPM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
JPM.loc[JPM['20 MA'] < JPM['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100
DJX.loc[DJX['20 MA'] >= DJX['50 MA'], 'Action'] = 100
DJX.loc[DJX['20 MA'] < DJX['50 MA'], 'Action'] = -100

# cumulative returns
AAPL['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(AAPL['ret']*AAPL['Action'])
IBM['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(IBM['ret']*IBM['Action'])
JPM['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(JPM['ret']*JPM['Action'])
DJX['cumulative'] = np.cumsum(DJX['ret']*DJX['Action'])

#intersection
AAPL['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))
IBM['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))
JPM['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))
DJX['intersect'] = np.zeros((len(AAPL),1))

idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(AAPL['20 MA'][49:] - AAPL['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
AAPL['intersect'].iloc[idx] = AAPL['20 MA'].iloc[idx]
idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(IBM['20 MA'][49:] - IBM['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
IBM['intersect'].iloc[idx] = IBM['20 MA'].iloc[idx]
idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(JPM['20 MA'][49:] - JPM['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
JPM['intersect'].iloc[idx] = JPM['20 MA'].iloc[idx]
idx = np.argwhere(np.diff(np.sign(DJX['20 MA'][49:] - DJX['50 MA'][49:]))).flatten() + 49
DJX['intersect'].iloc[idx] = DJX['20 MA'].iloc[idx]
